Reasoning: The paper discusses an open-source autonomous vehicle testbed that includes sensors, perception, planning, control, and networking software stacks. This falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO) and cyber-physical systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning algorithms for perception and planning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses the use of ROS (Robot Operating System) for software development, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL).
